{"tid":566244,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[10月新番]牙狼 VANISHING LINE","createTime":"2018-02-19T18:02:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T19:41:10.000Z","uid":6752,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f0ed2472db558c4ef9ba0956bfc2d85c14dc9b63","tid":566244,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T18:02:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DSmJTYOVwAA8BqQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDSmJTYOVwAA8BqQ.jpg&h=b1bb2b0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「VANISHING LINE」的劇情是在高度發展的城市羅素市，在鶯歌燕舞太平盛世的熱鬧街道中，卻隱藏著動搖世界的巨大陰謀。而很早就覺察到事情不對頭的索德為了揭露陰謀，不為人知的自己一個人投身到與黑惡勢力的鬥爭中。但是索德在戰鬥中得到的只有意義不明的關鍵字El Dorado(黃金鄉)，而在與惡勢力戰鬥中索德遇到了少女索菲，索菲是尋找自己失踪了哥哥留下了的神秘信息「黃金鄉」的意思，失去了哥哥的索菲與過去曾經失去了妹妹的索德，在El Dorado(黃金鄉)這個關鍵詞的引導下，感到了看不到的羈絆二人共同行動，開始了各自感情交錯的旅程。<br />\n<br />\nCV<br />\nソード：関智一<br />\nソフィ：釘宮理恵<br />\nルーク：島﨑信長<br />\nジーナ：小清水亜美<br />\nナイト：浪川大輔<br />\nクイーン：朴璐美<br />\nビジョップ：堀内賢雄<br />\nウェイトレス・チアキ：たかはし智秋<br />\nフェイロン：土師孝也<br />\nメイファン：高垣彩陽<br />\nミーア：岬優花<br />\n<br />\nザルバ：影山ヒロノブ"},{"pid":"698669e2fca408f29e502daa388434c128be7fd2","tid":566244,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T18:03:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1013fa0c328bbfd6b38500c2f7c4238ad9b2cae0","tid":566244,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T18:04:29.000Z","msg":"之前個post呢"},{"pid":"7e5dd4b853aded9fbc81d685ae1f550ee16d291a","tid":566244,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T18:07:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DVm7AR4VAAA6OZb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDVm7AR4VAAA6OZb.jpg&h=7669cb34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DVm7BEsVAAE68ep.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDVm7BEs